					"type": 23,
					"value": "- loadlevel WLD_Main_A\r\n- goto -307; 589\r\n- Skip through HAG_HagLair_EntranceDouble and Skip through HagLair_TalkingDoor if they play\r\n- Recruit origin(s) you want to test\r\n- Pick up a Whispering Mask and put it on\r\n- HAG_HagLair_PutOnMask will play. You'll then enter combat with your party members and this dialogue will play shortly after."
